@NODE VERSIONS "What's you WorkBench?"

There are now three versions of Amosaic!

v1.2     - This is the LAST an ONLY available version that can be used with WB
2.xx!!!   You MUST turn off inline images.  WHY?  Because WB2.xx does not have
DataType support that WB3.xx has.  Also this version is not that stable!

v1.2.1   - This  needs  WB 3.xx by "accident". This was mainly a bug-fix, with
improved stability.

