@NODE PRWB "WORKBENCH"

	WorkBench  3.0  or  better  is  needed  to get the most out of Mosaic,
because it uses @{"DataTypes" LINK ADDT} for almost everything you see and hear. You can use
WB  2.xx  but  you  will  miss  out  on  an  awful lot of pictures sounds etc,
virtually reduces Mosaic to an AmigaGuide from what I hear.

@ENDNODE

